235
00:22:37,179 --> 00:22:39,277
Hey, look, they've opened up that kiosk now.

236
00:22:39,499 --> 00:22:40,909
Aye, and where's Polly?

237
00:22:41,116 --> 00:22:44,204
...Will all passengers please assemble in the departure lounge.

238
00:23:20,788 --> 00:23:21,972
Packing cases!

239
00:23:23,559 --> 00:23:38,601
I'm quite sure the first thing you want to do when you get to Switzerland is write home to your parents... But in case you don't have time, Chameleon Tours have some postcards of Zurich ready for you to write here. When you've finished your postcards, give them back to me and we'll post them for you in Zurich.

240
00:23:39,952 --> 00:23:41,643
Eh, do you mind?

241
00:23:41,903 --> 00:23:42,863
